stu_tags: PARTICIPATION MATTERS  ACCESSIBLE OUTSIDE CLASS  SKIP CLASS? YOU WON\'T PASS.
comments: Its the most rewarding experience to be apart of the school newspaper. If you care about your community and your fellow peers then you should be taking this class. She\'s tough but its worth it. Ask yourself, "Can I handle constructive criticism and unnecessary stress?" Challenge yourself and take this class. Be ready 2 show what you are made of

tag_professor: ACCESSIBLE OUTSIDE CLASS (1)  Participation matters (1)  Skip class? You won\'t pass. (1)
comments: She is the best teacher ever!!!Yeah she could be tough but what do you expect it isn\'t high school.If you have the tendency to slack off and procrastinate don\'t take this class.Only take this class if you really want to be part something greater than just attending school.It\'s fun if you make it fun and don\'t fall for negative comments.:)

tag_professor: ACCESSIBLE OUTSIDE CLASS (1)  Participation matters (1)  Skip class? You won\'t pass. (1)
comments: Very helpful, often going out of her way to help us on her days off; generous with grades; a lot of students who deserved D or F got C or D instead; many students don\'t do enough work and still pass; she lets students make decisions about their newspaper; workload wasn\'t tough; reporters have 3 weeks to write a story in most cases
